// Tutorial 3 — Silence and prolongation
//
//   -   silence (takes 1 beat, like a note)
//   _   prolongation (extends the previous note by 1 beat)
//
// C4 _ = C4 held for 2 beats
// C4 - D4 = C4, 1 beat silence, then D4

@core
@controls
@alphabet.western:browser

S -> C4 _ _ D4 - E4 _ F4 G4 _ _ _
